      "description": "• 2 players | • 2 packs | • 10 minutes\r\n<br><strong>OBJECTIVE:</strong>\r\n<br>Best your opponent in a series of fast <em>Magic</em> games using only the cards in a single pack!\r\n<br><strong>GET READY:</strong>\r\n<br>Each player opens a pack and makes four face-down piles of three cards each using the <em>Magic</em> cards inside. Players make their piles with the goal of winning a series of <em>Magic</em> games with these modified rules:\r\n<br>Players start at 5 life, have infinite mana, and cannot lose by drawing from an empty library.\r\n<br><strong>LET'S PLAY:</strong>\r\n<br>Randomly determine who goes first. Each player chooses which pile their opponent will use for each round. Then both players draw all three of their cards and play a game of <em>Magic</em>. When a player loses a game, they get to go first in the next game.\r\n<br><strong>TO WIN:</strong>\r\n<br>The first player to win two games wins the match.",
